    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2006-03-16</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in Senate</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2006-03-27T19:49:31Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Authorizes the President, upon making specified determinations, to exempt a certain proposed cooperation agreement with India from requirements of the Atomic Energy Act of 1954 (AEC) regarding: (1) mandatory maintenance of International Atomic Energy Agency safeguards for nuclear materials in peaceful nuclear activities; (2) certain additional export criteria and procedures; and (3) conduct resulting in termination of nuclear exports. </p> <p>Renders any such determinations without effect if the President finds that India has detonated a nuclear explosive device after enactment of this Act.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
